# HiveAI Knowledge Refinery — Cursor Rules

## Project Overview
AI-powered research system that discovers URLs, crawls pages, extracts knowledge triples via LLM reasoning, builds a knowledge graph, generates prose "Golden Books", and publishes to Hive blockchain. Includes an AI chat interface ("Ask the Keeper") with multi-hop semantic RAG.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3.11, Flask, SQLAlchemy
- Dual database: PostgreSQL (with pgvector) or SQLite (with numpy vector search)
- LLM: Ollama (local, preferred) or OpenRouter (cloud)
- Embeddings: BGE-M3 via sentence-transformers
- Web crawling: crawl4ai (Playwright-based)
- Structured output: instructor + Pydantic
- Blockchain: beem (Hive)

